{"tid":20960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院通過提升美台軍事交流法案","createTime":"2016-12-03T15:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T18:32:53.000Z","uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e44edd0e27b2eaaf35e74c04a6819f18be0fc50","tid":20960,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bowenpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/161202202356_taiwan_army_parade_624x351_victorchan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbowenpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F161202202356_taiwan_army_parade_624x351_victorchan.jpg&h=5b47c19d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過《2017國防授權法案》，內容含有允許美國國防高級官員和現役軍人訪問台灣等。<br />\n<br />\n根據來自美國的報道，此一法案的1254節允許美國和台灣之間改善軍事關係和國防合作。<br />\n<br />\n據稱法案內容明定，美台每年應該至少進行一次「高級軍事交流」，並且應該在美國或者台灣進行。<br />\n<br />\n台灣媒體報道說，如果法案通過並經美國總統簽字成為法律，將突破目前美國高級國防官員和現役軍人不得訪問台灣的限制。<br />\n<br />\n法案內容同時也明確定出「高級軍事交流」、「高級軍事官員」以及「資深國防官員」的定義。<br />\n<br />\n另外法案也要求美國國防部在每個財政年度結束之前，向國會提報來自台灣的軍售要求以及美國對台軍售的項目。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院將在下周表決此一法案，如果通過，將送交白宮，待美國總統簽字成為法律。<br />\n<br />\n《國防授權法案》是國會監督國防預算的一部分，按照眾議院的新聞稿，通過的版本大幅度增加了美國政府所要求的預算。"},{"pid":"cdec3bceab7194d6eeefd1f5be3c0951b72af80d","tid":20960,"uid":40682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"小支支千祈唔好干預別國內政，說三道四呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5233ed2463b23e06cf01d24bd307463b5787d6de","tid":20960,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"係咪即係奧巴馬同trump 扯貓尾，呢頭聽電話民主黨議員嘈，嗰頭搵民主黨總統簽份嘢解除某啲禁令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17abde57563cbdc87844e6fd808ddbb568c4005","tid":20960,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"西侵會唔會轉頭又override左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08037af9e50958681d9c86716221ac0427e60c63","tid":20960,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪即係奧巴馬同trump 扯貓尾，呢頭聽電話民主黨議員嘈，嗰頭搵民主黨總統簽份嘢解除某啲禁令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能等埋 trump 上台先簽"},{"pid":"065d7856ba7908ee201a29c71ab5a6fed81bd86b","tid":20960,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西侵會唔會轉頭又override左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱先同小英傾完電話喎"},{"pid":"3e1352550f9d0bc341ec0d5424b475c91e6a36cd","tid":20960,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"法案有效期僅1年 料難高調交流<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20161202%2Ftcaa2_r.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6ed8c75d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f318293334935af576196b895a01966d81cbefe7","tid":20960,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法案有效期僅1年 料難高調交流<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20161202%2Ftcaa2_r.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6ed8c75d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n內地知名軍事評論員吳戈指國防授權法的有效期僅是一年"},{"pid":"e8d19a0de12555cb86d6a3972884501f5cdeb445","tid":20960,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/232134_a145e0162ef77853b4fba64718656015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F232134_a145e0162ef77853b4fba64718656015.jpg&h=d78d7bed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cda710f0eb0981d5961cad73d490f3cf30023ee","tid":20960,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法案有效期僅1年 料難高調交流<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20161202%2Ftcaa2_r.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6ed8c75d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Van/htm/News/20161202/tcaa2_r.htm</a></blockquote><br />\n內地知名軍事評論員吳戈指國防授權法的有效期僅是一年</blockquote><br />\n另外法案也要求美國國防部在<span style=\"color: red;\">每個財政年度結束</span>之前，向國會提報來自台灣的軍售要求以及美國對台軍售的項目。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1dd7ad9584f0851d27a4fd5eade6fc85ce2ae4","tid":20960,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小支支千祈唔好干預別國內政，說三道四呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環小心支那偷技術重要d"}]}